505
00:22:59,480 --> 00:23:01,079
Get me an outfit. Something baggy.

506
00:23:01,680 --> 00:23:02,680
That's it.

507
00:23:13,720 --> 00:23:14,720
Shi Yi.

508
00:23:14,839 --> 00:23:17,279
We received photos from Liu Tie Hao.

509
00:23:17,559 --> 00:23:18,559
What do you think?

510
00:23:19,279 --> 00:23:20,839
Judging from yesterday,

511
00:23:21,160 --> 00:23:23,440
Liu Tie Hao has no immediate plans to harm Hou Jue.

512
00:23:24,359 --> 00:23:26,400
He just wants you to worry,

513
00:23:27,200 --> 00:23:28,559
