516
00:23:36,240 --> 00:23:37,240
We shouldn't.

517
00:23:37,920 --> 00:23:39,359
It is my job to protect Hou Jue.

518
00:23:39,759 --> 00:23:40,799
Don't worry.

519
00:23:40,799 --> 00:23:43,119
I've been in more dangerous situations.

520
00:23:43,680 --> 00:23:45,279
Shi Yi, whatever you do,

521
00:23:45,279 --> 00:23:47,720
