522
00:23:49,160 --> 00:23:50,200
I understand.

523
00:23:52,680 --> 00:23:53,680
Mr. Ma.

524
00:23:54,960 --> 00:23:57,759
The text records and call logs you have right now...

525
00:23:57,960 --> 00:24:00,039
aren't enough to make a police report just yet.

526
00:24:00,480 --> 00:24:01,480
But keep them safe.

527
00:24:01,759 --> 00:24:03,039
Once they can be used as evidence,

528
00:24:03,279 --> 00:24:05,039
we'll make sure he gets what he deserves.

529
00:24:05,559 --> 00:24:07,440
Okay, don't worry. I will.

530
00:24:09,240 --> 00:24:10,319
Shi Yi.

531
00:24:11,039 --> 00:24:12,119
Thank you.

532
00:24:12,839 --> 00:24:13,920
It's my job.

533
00:24:42,279 --> 00:24:43,359
- Mr. Hou Junior. - Mr. Hou Junior.

534
00:25:44,240 --> 00:25:45,319
Li Chu.

535
00:25:45,920 --> 00:25:47,240
Are you looking for me, Mr. Wu?

536
00:25:47,240 --> 00:25:48,240
No.

537
00:25:48,440 --> 00:25:49,480
I'm looking for Da Peng.

538
00:25:51,240 --> 00:25:52,240
Nice bike.

539
00:25:52,400 --> 00:25:53,480
Yes.

540
00:25:57,319 --> 00:25:58,960
- What is it? Tell me. - Li Chu.

541
00:25:59,559 --> 00:26:00,599
You see...

542
00:26:01,440 --> 00:26:02,519
Well...

543
00:26:02,880 --> 00:26:04,519
What is it? Tell me.

544
00:26:05,839 --> 00:26:07,119
I'll be honest with you.

545
00:26:08,039 --> 00:26:10,559
I'm hoping to have a proper chat with Da Peng.

546
00:26:12,599 --> 00:26:14,599
Ying Nan heard a lot of rumors about Shi Yi...

547
00:26:14,599 --> 00:26:15,759
from other people.

548
00:26:16,680 --> 00:26:18,359
Even if they broke up for real,

549
00:26:18,799 --> 00:26:21,559
it's not right for Da Peng to bad-mouth Shi Yi.

550
00:26:21,920 --> 00:26:23,000
Don't you agree?

551
00:26:23,440 --> 00:26:24,480
Yes.

552
00:26:24,920 --> 00:26:26,079
Just end it on a good note.

553
00:26:27,279 --> 00:26:29,039
Young people make mistakes too.

554
00:26:29,039 --> 00:26:30,039
That's right.

555
00:26:30,039 --> 00:26:31,119
Listen, Mr. Wu.

556
00:26:31,319 --> 00:26:32,319
If I see Da Peng,

557
00:26:32,319 --> 00:26:33,799
I'll let him know.

558
00:26:34,279 --> 00:26:36,000
- Okay. See you later. - See you later.

559
00:26:36,160 --> 00:26:37,240
Ride safely.

560
00:26:37,440 --> 00:26:38,480
All right.

561
00:26:44,480 --> 00:26:45,519
Your turn.

562
00:26:46,839 --> 00:26:47,839
All for one.

563
00:26:49,559 --> 00:26:50,799
One for the books.

564
00:26:53,079 --> 00:26:54,160
One...

565
00:26:54,359 --> 00:26:55,440
One-hit wonder.

566
00:26:56,680 --> 00:26:58,200
One in a million.

567
00:27:00,279 --> 00:27:02,839
The joke is on you. One-trick pony.

568
00:27:04,519 --> 00:27:05,519
One...

569
00:27:08,440 --> 00:27:09,960
One-trick horse.

570
00:27:09,960 --> 00:27:11,000
You lose.

571
00:27:11,200 --> 00:27:12,279
Go and wash the dishes.

572
00:27:12,680 --> 00:27:13,759
Fine.

573
00:27:28,480 --> 00:27:29,799
Coming. I'll get the door.

574
00:27:35,880 --> 00:27:36,960
Who are you looking for?

575
00:27:36,960 --> 00:27:37,960
You are...

576
00:27:38,720 --> 00:27:39,799
Da Peng.

577
00:27:39,799 --> 00:27:40,839
Da Peng.

578
00:27:41,039 --> 00:27:42,039
Mr. Wu.

579
00:27:42,039 --> 00:27:43,039
Are you guys eating?

580
00:27:44,519 --> 00:27:45,960
- I'll come back another day. - It's fine.

581
00:27:46,119 --> 00:27:47,119
It's Shi Yi's dad.

582
00:27:48,680 --> 00:27:49,680
Mr. Wu,

583
00:27:49,960 --> 00:27:51,920
since you're already here, come on in.

584
00:27:52,160 --> 00:27:54,000
Yes. Come on in.

585
00:28:05,839 --> 00:28:06,839
Please have a seat, Mr. Wu.

586
00:28:07,680 --> 00:28:09,319
Go. Get him some water.

587
00:28:09,480 --> 00:28:10,519
The water is right there.

588
00:28:18,200 --> 00:28:19,400
Mr. Wu, have some water.

589
00:28:26,160 --> 00:28:29,240
I'm his girlfriend, Xue Mei.

590
00:28:29,480 --> 00:28:31,039
If you have something to say, just say it.

591
00:28:31,480 --> 00:28:33,160
Da Peng and I have been together for a long time.

592
00:28:33,160 --> 00:28:34,559
He doesn't keep anything from me.

593
00:28:34,680 --> 00:28:36,039
A long time?

594
00:28:39,319 --> 00:28:40,759
Mr. Wu, have you eaten?

595
00:28:43,079 --> 00:28:44,359
What are you afraid of?

596
00:28:47,200 --> 00:28:48,200
Mr. Wu.

597
00:28:48,640 --> 00:28:50,599
I know what you're here to say.

598
00:28:51,400 --> 00:28:53,640
I understand how you feel.

599
00:28:54,519 --> 00:28:55,759
But this?

600
00:28:55,759 --> 00:28:57,720
I'd like you to put yourself in our shoes.

601
00:28:57,960 --> 00:28:59,920
Look at the matter from Da Peng and my perspective.

602
00:29:00,880 --> 00:29:02,920
Your daughter probably told you...

603
00:29:04,079 --> 00:29:05,200
that I'm the third wheel.

604
00:29:05,920 --> 00:29:08,440
But I'm telling you now. I'm not.

605
00:29:09,039 --> 00:29:10,920
When I got together with Da Peng,

606
00:29:10,920 --> 00:29:12,160
they had already broken up.

607
00:29:13,839 --> 00:29:15,160
You had already broken up?

608
00:29:16,839 --> 00:29:18,119
As far as I know,

609
00:29:18,400 --> 00:29:20,039
the real reason they broke up...

610
00:29:20,039 --> 00:29:21,759
is that your daughter is too busy...

611
00:29:21,759 --> 00:29:23,000
to have any time for him.

612
00:29:24,039 --> 00:29:25,359
What he needs the most now is...

613
00:29:25,640 --> 00:29:28,559
someone who appreciates him and keeps him company.

614
00:29:28,920 --> 00:29:29,960
And I'm that person.

615
00:29:32,079 --> 00:29:33,440
I admire his talent.

616
00:29:33,920 --> 00:29:35,880
It's also because of my recommendation...

617
00:29:36,119 --> 00:29:37,920
that more people started to recognize his work.

618
00:29:39,759 --> 00:29:40,799
Mr. Wu,

619
00:29:41,079 --> 00:29:42,359
do you still think...

620
00:29:42,559 --> 00:29:43,799
I'm the third wheel?

621
00:29:44,680 --> 00:29:47,680
Da Peng, is that true?

622
00:29:51,880 --> 00:29:52,880
Say something.

623
00:29:53,160 --> 00:29:54,160
Be quiet.

624
00:29:55,359 --> 00:29:56,480
Da Peng, let me ask you.

625
00:29:58,000 --> 00:29:59,799
Why did you tell everyone...

626
00:30:00,400 --> 00:30:02,200
that Shi Yi was having an affair?

627
00:30:03,119 --> 00:30:04,279
I didn't, Mr. Wu.

628
00:30:04,279 --> 00:30:05,359
I didn't say anything like that.

629
00:30:05,359 --> 00:30:06,359
What about the others?

630
00:30:07,079 --> 00:30:09,160
Li Chu isn't the only one saying that.

631
00:30:09,519 --> 00:30:11,480
Mr. Wu, I swear. It wasn't me.

632
00:30:11,480 --> 00:30:12,519
That's great.

633
00:30:12,519 --> 00:30:13,559
Call them right now.

634
00:30:13,559 --> 00:30:14,720
Tell them he heard it wrong.

635
00:30:15,240 --> 00:30:16,880
You're the one who had an affair and changed.

636
00:30:17,799 --> 00:30:19,279
Is this really necessary?

637
00:30:19,279 --> 00:30:20,319
Yes, it is!

638
00:30:22,240 --> 00:30:23,359
Zhu Da Peng.

639
00:30:24,200 --> 00:30:27,200
I wanted to come and apologize to you.

640
00:30:27,559 --> 00:30:29,680
I hoped you'd be able to let it go.

641
00:30:30,240 --> 00:30:31,279
But who knew?

642
00:30:31,599 --> 00:30:32,759
Not only did you cheat on Shi Yi,

643
00:30:32,759 --> 00:30:34,359
but you also said things behind her back.

644
00:30:34,880 --> 00:30:36,079
You're despicable!

645
00:30:36,480 --> 00:30:37,559
You're framing my daughter.

646
00:30:37,559 --> 00:30:38,599
I won't allow it.

647
00:30:38,599 --> 00:30:41,680
Mr. Wu, I broke up with Shi Yi.

648
00:30:41,680 --> 00:30:43,039
I don't owe you anything.

649
00:30:43,039 --> 00:30:44,640
You came to my house uninvited,

650
00:30:44,640 --> 00:30:46,039
harassed me to do this and that,

651
00:30:46,039 --> 00:30:47,359
and hollered at my girlfriend.

652
00:30:47,359 --> 00:30:48,559
Is this appropriate?

653
00:30:48,759 --> 00:30:49,839
- Also, - You...

654
00:30:49,839 --> 00:30:51,880
why should I explain anything to them?

655
00:30:52,319 --> 00:30:54,720
Please leave, Mr. Wu.

656
00:30:56,279 --> 00:30:57,400
I trust Da Peng.

657
00:30:58,480 --> 00:31:00,400
You two rogues.

658
00:31:00,640 --> 00:31:01,640
Wu Tian Yi.

659
00:31:02,000 --> 00:31:04,200
I addressed you as Mr. Wu out of respect.

660
00:31:04,559 --> 00:31:05,799
You're embarrassing yourself.

661
00:31:05,799 --> 00:31:07,559
You even got yourself on the credit blacklist.

662
00:31:07,559 --> 00:31:09,680
What right do you have to lecture us?

663
00:31:09,680 --> 00:31:10,759
You're ridiculous.

664
00:31:10,960 --> 00:31:11,960
Is he in debt?

665
00:31:12,200 --> 00:31:14,039
I'm not. I don't go back on my word.

666
00:31:14,200 --> 00:31:15,640
I just haven't paid you back.

667
00:31:15,640 --> 00:31:16,680
- I... - That's enough.

668
00:31:17,079 --> 00:31:18,400
A father like you...

669
00:31:18,400 --> 00:31:20,000
can't possibly raise anything good.

670
00:31:20,160 --> 00:31:22,480
I told you to keep your distance from such people.

671
00:31:22,680 --> 00:31:23,720
You...

672
00:31:23,839 --> 00:31:26,839
Mr. Wu, I'm asking you to leave one last time.

673
00:31:29,200 --> 00:31:31,200
- Just leave. - Or I'll call the police.

674
00:31:31,480 --> 00:31:32,759
Adulterers!

675
00:31:36,319 --> 00:31:37,440
Look at him acting now.

676
00:31:38,079 --> 00:31:40,200
The door is over there, sir.

677
00:31:40,200 --> 00:31:41,279
Can you stop acting?

678
00:31:43,039 --> 00:31:44,119
Wu Tian Yi.

679
00:31:48,799 --> 00:31:49,880
Mr. Wu?

680
00:31:50,680 --> 00:31:51,720
Mr. Wu.

681
00:31:52,400 --> 00:31:53,440
- Mr. Wu. - Mr. Wu.

682
00:31:53,880 --> 00:31:55,279
Hurry! Call 120!

683
00:31:56,880 --> 00:31:59,559
Mr. Wu.

684
00:32:00,960 --> 00:32:02,640
(Emergency rescue)

685
00:32:14,519 --> 00:32:15,640
Heaven protects. It will keep you safe.

686
00:32:15,640 --> 00:32:17,160
- Please make way. - Move.

687
00:32:23,440 --> 00:32:25,319
What are you waiting for? Family members can get in.

688
00:32:25,319 --> 00:32:27,920
No. I'm not family.

689
00:32:28,240 --> 00:32:29,319
You're not his family?

690
00:32:29,440 --> 00:32:32,200
But I can give you the contact information of his family.

691
00:32:33,160 --> 00:32:34,240
All right then. Hurry.

692
00:32:53,759 --> 00:32:56,759
(Hou Jue)

693
00:33:03,200 --> 00:33:04,200
Hello?

694
00:33:04,440 --> 00:33:06,000
Are you Wu Tian Yi's family?

695
00:33:06,000 --> 00:33:07,079
Yes, I am.

696
00:33:07,920 --> 00:33:09,799
He had a heart attack. They're saving him right now.

697
00:33:10,160 --> 00:33:11,200
What?

698
00:33:11,640 --> 00:33:13,240
He needs surgery right away.

699
00:33:13,240 --> 00:33:14,359
Please come as soon as possible.

700
00:33:15,920 --> 00:33:18,000
The thing is, I'm busy right now.

701
00:33:18,319 --> 00:33:20,599
I'm not sure when I'll be able to get back.

702
00:33:21,519 --> 00:33:24,279
Doctor, please save my dad first.

703
00:33:25,000 --> 00:33:26,119
I'll call my supervisor.

704
00:33:26,119 --> 00:33:27,160
He'll send someone.

705
00:33:27,559 --> 00:33:29,160
All right. Be quick.

706
00:33:29,160 --> 00:33:30,720
Okay, thank you.

707
00:33:47,240 --> 00:33:48,960
I hope her dad is okay.

708
00:33:50,480 --> 00:33:52,160
Otherwise, we won't be able to explain ourselves.

709
00:33:52,319 --> 00:33:53,440
That's for sure.

710
00:33:54,680 --> 00:33:56,359
You shouldn't have talked back.

711
00:33:56,559 --> 00:33:57,599
I couldn't stop you.

712
00:33:57,599 --> 00:33:58,960
You're scolding me?

713
00:33:58,960 --> 00:34:00,119
You're the one to talk.

714
00:34:00,599 --> 00:34:01,920
Didn't you say you two already broke up...

715
00:34:01,920 --> 00:34:03,279
when we got together?

716
00:34:03,279 --> 00:34:04,279
Yes.

717
00:34:04,279 --> 00:34:06,039
Then why did you say that about Shi Yi to others?

718
00:34:06,240 --> 00:34:07,359
I did not.

719
00:34:18,769 --> 00:34:20,519
I hope it's nothing serious.

720
00:34:20,519 --> 00:34:22,360
I sure hope so.

721
00:34:22,679 --> 00:34:24,639
It'd be a huge problem if Shi Yi pursued the matter.

722
00:34:24,920 --> 00:34:26,329
I regret yelling at him.

723
00:34:26,440 --> 00:34:27,920
I didn't think he'd collapse so easily.

724
00:34:28,920 --> 00:34:31,039
Is what you said earlier true then?

725
00:34:32,000 --> 00:34:33,000
Yes.

726
00:34:33,119 --> 00:34:34,329
Then it's fine.

727
00:34:34,559 --> 00:34:36,289
If you hadn't told him the truth,

728
00:34:36,289 --> 00:34:38,039
how else could you have shut him up?

729
00:34:38,639 --> 00:34:39,769
The way I saw it,

730
00:34:39,880 --> 00:34:41,559
he would've fought us until the bitter end.

731
00:35:40,400 --> 00:35:42,809
Loser, your champion is here.

